{"tid":1931373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Expats喺香港平均每個月賺117000 HKD","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T04:43:05.000Z","uid":312242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bed9e3705412169a10f5ad44726c395d970d04","tid":1931373,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"The global Expat Explorer Survey, which comprised 22,318 respondents from 163 countries and territories, found that expats in Hong Kong earn an average salary of US$178,706 (HK$1.4 million), which is US$72,000 more than the average expat globally.<br />\n<br />\n成班奶共寄生蟲賺平均香港人嘅錢十倍, 住大屋, 每日去fine dining, 每日屌新港女，仲唔戴口罩播毒。<br />\n<br />\n嗰班垃圾係警察指揮官, CEO, ibankers。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋係嚟香港賺錢, 目標同支那人一致</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/oo0z6Es.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Foo0z6Es.jpg&h=bb7d6aa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58bd948b8ff23c8fc935da117b7181dd17a5c803","tid":1931373,"uid":351758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f46f53c2d27ab42b588117693047d604b8eec56","tid":1931373,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bd948b8ff23c8fc935da117b7181dd17a5c803","tid":1931373,"uid":351758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"當亞洲人喺美國努力賺錢嘅時候， 班垃圾under qualified睇到就嚟亞洲freeride 做有錢人, 屌港女, 吃喝玩樂, 炒樓, 播毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAq8A5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAq8A5i.jpg&h=0783503b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513e8fba3753bda96c682448e0a882a6ef1bfb76","tid":1931373,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"expat賺得多好正常<br />\n垃圾水平本身唔會出到國去國際金融中心嘅跨國公司做高層<br />\n<br />\n不過班友自大睇低本地人死都唔戴口罩播毒先係問題<br />\n外國女人去回教國家都識包頭都唔會同當地人噪包頭有無作用<br />\n因為入鄉隨俗本身就係禮貌同尊重<br />\n但對香港人就一於少理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea576568bfb9fb0eda7698dc1a773c1f87ca85bf","tid":1931373,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"513e8fba3753bda96c682448e0a882a6ef1bfb76","tid":1931373,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"expat賺得多好正常<br />\n垃圾水平本身唔會出到國去國際金融中心嘅跨國公司做高層<br />\n<br />\n不過班友自大睇低本地人死都唔戴口罩播毒先係問題<br />\n外國女人去回教國家都識包頭都唔會同當地人噪包頭有無作用<br />\n因為入鄉隨俗本身就係禮貌同尊重<br />\n但對香港人就一於少理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"所以班垃圾同支那人level差唔多<br />\n<br />\n要攬炒嘅, 班垃圾係無可避免嘅目標, 因為佢哋控制香港好多戰略經濟地位"},{"pid":"1bffb1a21676d872f7ab0d971594b0ca7e6ab4b6","tid":1931373,"uid":102536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"竟然無人覆呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}